<item>
<title>Unsafe at Any Speed: The Designed-In Dangers of DevSecOps</title>
<link>https://www.SwATips.com/articles/20260126.html</link>
<pubDate>Mon, 26 Jan 2026 00:00:00 -0600</pubDate>
<description><![CDATA[

