 <div class="author" style="margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box;"><span class="ec-lmr-12" style="margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box;">Jon Hood</span></div><br style="margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box;">
<div class="date" style="margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box;"><span class="ec-lmr-12" style="margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box;">Monday 12</span><sup class="textsuperscript" style="margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box;"><span class="ec-lmr-9" style="margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box;">th</span></sup><span class="ec-lmr-12" style="margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box;"> May, 2025</span></div>
